}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== A company named ''Shenzhenshi Suofei Kejiyouxian Gongsi limited'' submitted a FCC Change of Identification Request on June 24th, 2019 to establish [http://fccid.io/2ATNNMFM3 2ATNNMFM3] from [http://fccid.io/V7TMESH5 V7TMESH5] of the [[Tenda nova MW5 (Mesh5)|Tenda Mesh5]].
Top-side marking for the Winbond W25Q64JVSSIQ flash is 25Q64JVSIQ.
